---
model: googleai/gemini-2.0-flash
config:
  temperature: 0.7
  maxOutputTokens: 2048
  topK: 40
  topP: 0.95
  stopSequences:
    - "END"
    - "STOP"
input:
  schema:
    name: string, The user's name
    topic: string, Topic to write about
    style?: "formal" | "casual" | "technical"
    wordCount?: integer, Target word count
output:
  format: json
  schema:
    article:
      title: string
      content: string
      wordCount: integer
      tags: string[]
---

{{! This prompt demonstrates advanced schema definitions with Picoschema }}

{{role "system"}}
You are an expert content writer named {{name}}.

WRITING GUIDELINES:
{{#if style}}
- Write in a {{style}} style
{{else}}
- Write in a professional but approachable style
{{/if}}

{{#if wordCount}}
- Target approximately {{wordCount}} words
{{/if}}

{{role "user"}}
Write an article about: {{topic}}

Return a JSON response with title, content, wordCount, and relevant tags.
